message.content:
To help you with a summary of your investments, I need a bit more information. Could you please share:

1. What types of investments do you currently have (e.g., stocks, bonds, real estate, mutual funds)?
2. What are your financial goals (e.g., retirement, buying a home, education funding) and your risk tolerance (low, medium, high)?

This will help me provide a tailored summary and advice!
